body: next_current - {context.forecast_next.precipitation_current}. next_next_current - {context.forecast_next_next.precipitation_current}. weather_condition - {context.weather_forecast.condition}. next_condition - {context.forecast_next.condition}. next_next_condition - {context.forecast_next_next.condition}. next_day_part - {context.forecast_next.day_part}. next_next_day_part - {context.forecast_next_next.day_part}. weather_day_part - {context.weather_forecast.day_part}. precipitation_day_part - {context.precipitation_day_part}. precipitation_change_hours - {context.precipitation_change_hours}. precipitation_next_change_hours - {context.precipitation_next_change_hours}. precipitation_next_day_part - {context.precipitation_next_day_part}. precipitation_next_next_change_hours - {context.precipitation_next_next_change_hours}. precipitation_next_next_day_part - {context.precipitation_next_next_day_part}.
context:
1      {% macro __render_next_condition(context, level) -%}
  2        {% if context.forecast_next is defined and context.forecast_next and context.forecast_next_next is defined and context.forecast_next_next -%}
  3          {%- if context.precipitation_debug is defined and context.precipitation_debug is not none -%}
  4 -->>       {{ '\n' }}
  5 -->>       next_current - {{ context.forecast_next.precipitation_current }}.
  6 -->>       next_next_current - {{ context.forecast_next_next.precipitation_current }}.
  7 -->>       weather_condition - {{ context.weather_forecast.condition }}.
  8 -->>       next_condition - {{ context.forecast_next.condition }}.
  9 -->>       next_next_condition - {{ context.forecast_next_next.condition }}.
 10 -->>       next_day_part - {{ context.forecast_next.day_part }}.
 11 -->>       next_next_day_part - {{ context.forecast_next_next.day_part }}.
 12 -->>       weather_day_part - {{ context.weather_forecast.day_part }}.
 13 -->>       precipitation_day_part - {{ context.precipitation_day_part }}.
 14 -->>       precipitation_change_hours - {{ context.precipitation_change_hours }}.
 15 -->>       precipitation_next_change_hours - {{ context.precipitation_next_change_hours }}.
 16 -->>       precipitation_next_day_part - {{ context.precipitation_next_day_part }}.
 17 -->>       precipitation_next_next_change_hours - {{ context.precipitation_next_next_change_hours }}.
 18 -->>       precipitation_next_next_day_part - {{ context.precipitation_next_next_day_part }}.
 19 -->>       {{ '\n' }}
